  <h1>About kloopik</h1>

  <p>kloopik is a free browser gaming platform built around a simple idea: great games should be one click away. No downloads, no installs, no accounts required — just pick a game and play.</p>

  <p>We hand-pick and build arcade classics and casual games that run entirely in your browser using modern web standards. Every game on kloopik is playable on desktop and mobile, on any device with a modern browser.</p>

  <h2>Our games</h2>
  <p>We currently offer games across eight categories: Arcade, Puzzle, Card, Action, Strategy, Runner, Sports, and Shooting. We add new games regularly — check the <a href="/new/">New Games</a> page for the latest additions.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions or feedback? Reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@kloopik.com">hello@kloopik.com</a>.</p>
